snippet.textDisplay:
While Guy still wins by a large margin, the comparison to naruto's chakra bomb isn't really accurate. Naruto has an absolute fuckton of chakra, even in base. For example, the cloud village made a cannon that required the chakra of 50-100 jonin teir ninja to destroy the moon. During the war arc Naruto granted enough chakra to the remaining members of the shinobi alliance to give them 3 times Kakashi's (a jonin) base chakra, and still had more than enough to fight off the 10 tails and Obito. So needless to say, taking all of that pure chakra and detonating it has massive devastating power. Guy went all out fighting Madara, meanwhile Naruto was low on chakra for the first half of the fight and was primarily using ninjutsu which madara was resistant to.

Guy still wins tho, the man kicked hard enough to make space a solid object.
